    <item>
      <title>特朗普总统的关税已加强了中国的出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-s-tariffs-have-rerouted-china-s-exports-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统对关税的征收促使中国制造商和出口商寻求替代市场，例如印度尼西亚和墨西哥。正如Katia Dmitrieva在彭博电视台报道的那样，中国商品的涌入正在影响这些新兴经济体。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-20/trump-s-tariffs-have-rerouted-china-s-exports-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率，因为关税会加热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美联储应降低利率，并随着官员的税率付出的经济成本而与美国中央银行分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股票向香港同行准备2020-low</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/chinese-shares-premium-to-hong-kong-peers-poised-for-2020-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国大陆股票与香港列出的同行之间的价格差距有望达到四年以上的低点，因为对人工智能的乐观情绪驱使投资者进入该市市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/chinese-shares-premium-to-hong-kong-peers-poised-for-2020-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 01:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国银行将其基准贷款率五个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/chinese-banks-hold-their-benchmark-lending-rates-for-fifth-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在没有更多货币宽松的情况下，中国银行将其连续五个月的基准贷款利率持有，因为官员在美国关税再次上升的情况下留下了刺激的开放空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/chinese-banks-hold-their-benchmark-lending-rates-for-fifth-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 01:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受特朗普的关税威胁加剧的铜付出了10,000美元的集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/copper-climbs-above-10-000-a-ton-as-us-buyers-ramp-up-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数周的全球贸易错位，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对关键工业金属的关税触发了数周的全球贸易错位，铜越过了其每吨10,000美元的关键门槛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/copper-climbs-above-10-000-a-ton-as-us-buyers-ramp-up-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 01:03:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
